addition, the collisional strength $Q_{\\rm\nD}^*$ even for kilometer-sized or smaller bodies affects the growth of cores;\n$Q_{\\rm D}^* \\gtrsim 10^7 \\,{\\rm erg/g}$ for bodies $\\lesssim 1$ km is likely\nfor this gas giant formation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 19 Jun 2018 17:31:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-08"}
