 were buggy and harmful for reuse. Furthermore, we found\n214 code snippets that could potentially violate the license of their original\nsoftware and appear 7,112 times in 2,427 GitHub projects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Jun 2018 10:43:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Apr 2019 18:32:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-04-03"}
